# atlas-conceptor — base model for the Sacred Concepts Atlas agents
# Build:   ollama create atlas-conceptor -f modelfiles/atlas-conceptor.Modelfile
# Upgrade path (RTX 4090): change FROM to qwen3:14b (or qwen3:32b) and raise num_ctx.
#
# This Modelfile is deliberately thin: ONE loaded model serves BOTH agent roles
# (router and classifier) so the 3060 never thrashes between weights. The
# doctrine lives in versioned prompt files sent as system messages per call:
#   doctrine_core.md + router_role.md      -> router (think=off)
#   doctrine_core.md + classifier_role.md  -> classifier (think=on)
# Their sha256 is recorded in runs.prompts_sha. Sampling defaults below are
# Qwen3 thinking-mode settings (see STRATEGY doc section 6); the orchestrator
# overrides per role (router uses non-thinking settings: temp 0.7, top_p 0.8).

FROM qwen3:8b

PARAMETER temperature 0.6
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER top_k 20
PARAMETER min_p 0.0
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.0
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
